track.name: I'll Take Care Of You
comments: Beth Hart is one of the most exciting blues singers of our time, with an expressive and powerful, slightly husky voice and a real talent to pass through it all kinds of feelings and emotions.
It feels good to hear someone say, “Take care.” But it feels so much better to hear someone say, “I will take care of you'' .~ they're great ! [2]
Wow.... second cut by her today. I care nothing about Bonamassa, but her voice is magical.

Contemporary American blues singer and songwriter Beth Hart in her works shows a romantic mood, bright sound, the depth of life. All of this leaves a lot of space for imagination and excitement. Get inspired :)
It feels good to hear someone say, “Take care.” But it feels so much better to hear someone say, “I will take care of you.~ they're great !
Powerful voice of Beth ------ Love this work
Live in the clouds, or at least once to get there everyone dreams, but the musician practically lives there in his work.
Best female singer I've heard in a long time.
Some songs leave you wanting more. They all should.
